{"tid":628410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲爆乳人妻　用柔道「袈裟固」逮捕小偷","createTime":"2018-04-13T22:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T09:44:20.000Z","uid":4075,"like":128,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"997089a335d7a100b001d0792135af50b7d1adfc","tid":628410,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:58:29.000Z","msg":"日本警官的妻子擅長柔道，日前前往神社參拜的時候遇到香油錢小偷，於是用柔道技法將小偷壓制在地後，打電話報警將小偷逮捕。<br />\n據《產經新聞》報導，11日早上10點20四，日本埼玉縣一處的神社，有位44歲男子田中俊明偷香油錢後，準備騎停在附近腳踏車逃跑，當時參拜中的一名男子目擊到後大喊「你絕對逃不掉的」，並大喊請附近民眾幫忙，30歲山形麻理子聽到後立即上前詢問「發生什麼事情了」，知道是小偷後，立即衝上前，先用柔道投技「大腰」將田中俊明摔倒，再使用「袈裟固」進行壓制，確認田中俊明無法逃脫後，再請目擊男子打電話報警。<br />\n山形麻理子指出，因為她丈夫是巡査部長，常聽丈夫說不能容許犯罪，加上她自己也是前警員，所以自己也有同樣的使命感，才會出手制止小偷。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180413/1334022/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180413%2F1334022%2F&d=W7b%2BWNj1u%2BV7aCy48ljdWxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c7a98a4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180413%2F1334022%2F&h=8515826d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180413/1334022/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242e7f757f1dc75ee651602aad7672ef2a4aaa26","tid":628410,"uid":48286,"like":127,"dislike":48,"score":79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T23:01:09.000Z","msg":"妖，你貼埋幅圖得唔得！"},{"pid":"a2510656d13df3d633ae0f0869468831e5ebe0e6","tid":628410,"uid":28619,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T23:01:25.000Z","msg":"新av題材"},{"pid":"3602ac2a7b5ec4ee623cbad25d6da4681ac047f7","tid":628410,"uid":43470,"like":391,"dislike":2,"score":389,"quote":{"pid":"242e7f757f1dc75ee651602aad7672ef2a4aaa26","tid":628410,"uid":48286,"like":127,"dislike":48,"score":79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2